    { title: 'More intruiging than you think..', image_url: 'Harvey_Wallbanger.jpg', drink_name: 'Harvey Wallbanger', date: '2017, 3, 12', body: "The only thing worse than yellow snow is green snow. You better get your coat out, this is going to be a cold painting. Let your heart be your guide. How do you make a round circle with a square knife? That's your challenge for the day. Follow the lay of the land. It's most important. You can't have light without dark. You can't know happiness unless you've known sorrow.  Maybe there's a little something happening right here. Let's have a little bit of fun today. There it is. You can't make a mistake. Anything that happens you can learn to use - and make something beautiful out of it.  We'll put some happy little leaves here and there. We artists are a different breed of people. We're a happy bunch. Isn't that fantastic? And just raise cain. Trees grow however makes them happy.",
