    { title: 'Classy and Bitter', image_url: 'negroni.jpg', drink_name: 'Negroni', date: '2017, 2, 20', body: "Just relax and let it flow. That easy. You can do anything your heart can imagine. Imagination is the key to painting.  You can get away with a lot. Even the worst thing we can do here is good. You need the dark in order to show the light. Now then, let's play. Every day I learn. Do an almighty painting with us.  I think there's an artist hidden in the bottom of every single one of us. Brown is such a nice color. Put light against light - you have nothing. Put dark against dark - you have nothing. It's the contrast of light and dark that each give the other one meaning. We'll do another happy little painting. You are only limited by your imagination.  You don't have to spend all your time thinking about what you're doing, you just let it happen. But we're not there yet, so we don't need to worry about it. Only think about one thing at a time. Don't get greedy. A fan brush is a fantastic piece of equipment. Use it. Make friends with it. Use absolutely no pressure. Just like an angel's wing.",
